⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Dr. Serge Leveque
node COR · COR · ⟦Dr. Serge Leveque:COR:69344c⟧

WHO   — Dr. Serge Leveque — the family man
WHAT  — The crew's warm center and nuclear hand — a family man who calculates the charges and gives his life in the deep so the mission can continue.
WHERE — COR · The Core  Framework inputs: The Core (2003, dir. Jon Amiel)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the people who die on these missions had whole lives elsewhere, and the film insists we feel the one it takes.
HOW   — By weapons expertise, a steady warmth, and a sacrifice made with his family's photo close.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I built the bombs that might save the world — and I left my children's faces behind to set them right.

